China to Introduce Yuan Investment Rules This Year, 21st Herald Reports

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-06-22T22:54:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-22/china-to-introduce-yuan-investment-rules-this-year-21st-herald-reports.html
China ’s central bank aims to
introduce yuan-denominated foreign direct investment rules this
year, the 21st Century Business Herald reported today, citing an
unidentified official at the People’s Bank of China’s monetary
policy department.  The central bank will limit investments in companies
operating in industries that are in oversupply, and also in
banks, insurers and securities companies, the newspaper
reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
